@startuml domain-import-module
title SafeCrowd Domain Import Module (Open-Source Stack)

left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

package "application" {
  [Import Workflow UI\n(file select / review / accept)] as ImportUi
}

package "domain" {
  package "api" {
    [ImportOrchestrator\n(single import entry)] as Orchestrator
    [ImportResult\n(layout / issues / trace refs)] as ImportResult
  }

  package "adapters" {
    [DxfImportService\n(libdxfrw)] as DxfImport
    [IfcImportService\n(IfcOpenShell)] as IfcImport
  }

  package "transform" {
    [RawImportModel\n(source entities / units /\nlayer or GUID refs)] as RawImportModel
    [GeometryNormalizer\n(Clipper2 / Boost.Geometry)] as GeometryNormalizer
    [CanonicalGeometry\n(floors / walls / portals /\nobstacles / vertical links)] as CanonicalGeometry
    [FacilityLayoutBuilder\n(zone / connection /\nbarrier inference)] as FacilityLayoutBuilder
    [FacilityLayout\n(zones / links / controls /\nvalidation targets)] as FacilityLayout
    [ImportValidationService\n(disconnected areas /\nmissing exits / width checks)] as ImportValidation
    [ImportArtifactStore\n(trace refs / user overrides /\nreimport metadata)] as ImportArtifactStore
  }

  package "navigation bake" {
    [NavigationBakeService\n(Recast / Detour)] as NavigationBake
    [BakedNavigationData\n(navmesh / path queries /\nspawn-goal anchors)] as BakedNavigationData
  }

  [SimulationSession\n(domain run orchestration)] as SimulationSession
}

package "engine" {
  [EngineRuntime\n(control)] as EngineRuntime
  [EngineWorld\n(resources / commands)] as EngineWorld
}

ImportUi --> Orchestrator : import file / choose rules
Orchestrator --> DxfImport : .dxf
Orchestrator --> IfcImport : .ifc
DxfImport --> RawImportModel
IfcImport --> RawImportModel
RawImportModel --> GeometryNormalizer
GeometryNormalizer --> CanonicalGeometry
CanonicalGeometry --> FacilityLayoutBuilder
FacilityLayoutBuilder --> FacilityLayout
FacilityLayout --> ImportValidation
ImportValidation --> ImportResult : layout + issues
FacilityLayout --> ImportArtifactStore : save trace / overrides
FacilityLayout --> NavigationBake
NavigationBake --> BakedNavigationData
ImportResult --> ImportUi : review / approve / retry
ImportResult --> SimulationSession : accepted layout
BakedNavigationData --> SimulationSession : runtime-ready nav data
SimulationSession --> EngineRuntime : initialize run
SimulationSession --> EngineWorld : register resources

note bottom of Orchestrator
  Domain boundary for import.
  Application passes only file path
  and review decisions.
  External SDK types do not escape.
end note

note bottom of ImportArtifactStore
  Reimport stability lives here:
  source handles, GUIDs, user edits,
  and mapping decisions are preserved
  outside engine state.
end note

note bottom of EngineWorld
  Engine receives plain domain resources only.
  No libdxfrw, IfcOpenShell, Recast,
  or Detour headers should be exposed
  through engine-facing contracts.
end note

note bottom of NavigationBake
  DetourCrowd is runtime behavior support,
  not an import dependency,
  so it is intentionally excluded here.
end note

@enduml
